      "widgets_values": [
        "# 🔽 Recommended Upscaler Models\n\n## 🧍 Realistic Upscaling\n**Model:** [4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth](https://openmodeldb.info/models/4x-NMKD-Siax-CX)\n\n> 📌 Great for photorealistic details, portraits, and general video/photo upscaling.\n\n---\n\n## 🧑‍🎨 Anime Upscaling\n**Model:** [4x-AnimeSharp.pth](https://huggingface.co/utnah/esrgan/blob/main/4x-AnimeSharp.pth)\n\n> 📌 Works well on clean anime lines, flat shading, and cel-style art. Pairs well with stylized anime outputs.\n\n---\n\n## 📁 Where to Place These\n- Drop the `.pth` model files into your `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models` folder.\n- Restart ComfyUI if models don’t appear in the dropdowns.\n"
      ],
      "color": "#332922",
      "bgcolor": "#593930"
